License: UNKNOWN
Description: # Ghost-translator
        A little tool that generates a translation key file for a ghost theme
        
        ## Usage
        
        While in a Ghost theme folder, use:
        ```
        ghost_translator
        ```
        
        
        ## Installation
        ```
        pip install ghost_translator
        ```
        
